text: TrustoCorp is an artist or a group of artists based in New York City. They are known for their humorous street signshttps://abcnews.go.com/WN/mysterious- funny-american-street-signs/story?id=10162700 and product labels,http://consumerist.com/2010/04/buy-yourself-a-nose-job-in-a-can-a- bulimia-bar.html which can be found in New York City, San Francisco, San Diego, and Miami. Internationally their signs have been seen in Newcastle- Upon-Tyne United Kingdom. ==References== Category:Artists from New York (state)
